AUDIO: 'Here\'s how to create a next-level music and sound effects track for your next video or film project using your voice, Suno\'s cover feature, and Suno\'s sound effects feature. Welcome back to the channel where we discuss the creative uses of AI. And instead of just typing in one long prompt and hoping that it\'s'

[00:13] [scene:talk]
