VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'with sound effects and music. Now, the process is not automatic, but it\'s also not rocket science. And if you\'ve never thought to try this, I invite you to try this technique out. So, let\'s see how it works. Let\'s dive into how to do this by looking at an actual use case where I'

